{"title":"Linux的几个有趣命令","date":"2018-06-14T14:53:09.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2018年6月14日","L":"2018/06/14","MM-DD":"06-14"},"link":"2018/06/linux-funny-commond","categories":["Linux"],"updated":"2020-09-19T16:09:59.717Z","content":"<h4 id=\"sl命令\">sl命令<a title=\"#sl命令\" href=\"#sl命令\"></a></h4>\n<p>你会看到一辆小货车从屏幕右边开到了左边～</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">安装：sudo apt-get install sl</span><br><span class=\"line\">运行：sl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"fortune命令\">fortune命令<a title=\"#fortune命令\" href=\"#fortune命令\"></a></h4>\n<p>输出一句话，有笑话、名言、唐诗宋词等等：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">安装：sudo apt-get install fortune</span><br><span class=\"line\">运行：fortune</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"cowsay命令\">cowsay命令<a title=\"#cowsay命令\" href=\"#cowsay命令\"></a></h4>\n<p>用ASCII字符打印牛、羊等动物。还有<code>cowthink</code>命令，这是是奶牛想，命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">安装：sudo apt-get install cowsay</span><br><span class=\"line\">运行：cowsay -f tux &quot;坑爹啊～&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">cowsay -l    查看其他动物的名字</span><br><span class=\"line\">cowsay -f 动物们 &quot;坑爹啊～&quot;    可其他动物</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"cmatrix命令\">cmatrix命令<a title=\"#cmatrix命令\" href=\"#cmatrix命令\"></a></h4>\n<p>这个是《黑客帝国》里面的代码雨，很cool：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">安装：sudo apt-get install cmatrix</span><br><span class=\"line\">运行：cmatrix</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>使用<code>Ctrl+C</code>程序结束。</p>\n<h4 id=\"figlet、toilet命令\">figlet、toilet命令<a title=\"#figlet、toilet命令\" href=\"#figlet、toilet命令\"></a></h4>\n<p>艺术字生成器，由ASCII字符组成，把文本显示成标题栏。此外还有banner这个命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">安装：sudo apt-get install figlet</span><br><span class=\"line\">    sudo apt-get install toilet</span><br><span class=\"line\">运行：figlet I LOVE YOU !</span><br><span class=\"line\">    toilet I LOVE YOU !</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>此外<code>toilet</code>还可以添加颜色</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">toilet -f mono -F gay I LOVE YOU !</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"oneko命令\">oneko命令<a title=\"#oneko命令\" href=\"#oneko命令\"></a></h4>\n<p>这个也比较有趣，桌面上出现一只喵星人，会跟着你的鼠标再跑，<code>Ctrl+C</code>结束：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">安装：sudo apt-get install oneko</span><br><span class=\"line\">运行：oneko</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"yes命令\">yes命令<a title=\"#yes命令\" href=\"#yes命令\"></a></h4>\n<p>一直输出字符，使用<code>Ctrl+C</code>结束：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yes I LOVE YOU !</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h4 id=\"cal命令\">cal命令<a title=\"#cal命令\" href=\"#cal命令\"></a></h4>\n<p>这个是打印日历：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cal 6 2018</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"结尾\">结尾<a title=\"#结尾\" href=\"#结尾\"></a></h1>\n<p>这些命令是在今日头条看到的，很有趣。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"根据转载的一篇文章总结的Java学习方法","link":"2018/06/java-learning-method"},"next":{"title":"在Linux中使配置alias永久生效","link":"2018/06/alise-linux"},"plink":"https://www.shiguangping.com/2018/06/linux-funny-commond/","toc":[{"id":"结尾","title":"结尾","index":"1"}]}